Description: Provides utility functions that extend the capabilities of the rbmi
             package to support clinical trial analysis workflows. 
             Includes tools for manipulating imputed data, applying analysis 
             methods across imputations, and generating output compatible with 
             clinical data standards.
Maintainer: Mark Baillie <bailliem@gmail.com>
